GSD.description:
btrfs: always report error in run_one_delayed_ref()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.165 by commit 18bd1c9c02e64a3567f90c83c2c8b855531c8098. For more details please see the references link.
